==Japanese==
===Etymology===
{{ja-kanjitab-top}}
! [[早]] || [[月]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
From [[早]] (さ, ''sa''), "early" + [[苗]] (なえ, ''nae'', "sprouts") + [[月]] (つき, ''tsuki'', "month")

===Noun===
'''早月''' ([[さつき]], ''satsuki'')

# {{archaic}} the fifth month of the lunar calendar
# {{poetic}} the month of planting rice; the month of [[May]]

